name: n1ght | first translation | Effy To
description: The sun does not rise light years away; all of the energy from the sun was harvested and used to produce music. Music is energy, they don't need the sun in order for plants to grow or for people to be healthy. The energy of the sun is changed into musical energy. This is called Audiosynthesis. Their sun actually doesn't exist anymore. It was used up by galactic musicians, and now they are here! The sun of the milky way is the next sun to be used for these epic tracks.
